            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 繼上年推出的 MOMENTUM 4 Wireless 後，再次推出新款無線藍牙頭戴式耳機 ACCENTUM Wireless。小編用後就覺得承傳了 Sennheiser 舒服的音色，價錢方面屬中價位，但表現似乎不差過旗艦耳機，整體性價比都幾高。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1205322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>黑白兩色，低調設計不易留痕</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 的設計及外觀頗為簡潔直觀，整個耳機只有側面印有細小的 Sennheiser 標示，小編頗喜歡低調的設計。機身用上了磨砂質地，不易留下指紋等污漬。機底有個 USB-C 充電位。ACCENTUM Wireless 有 2 款顏色選擇，小編拿到的是黑色，型格之選。另外還有白色，感覺優雅高貴，比較會適合女士。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1205326 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整個耳機只有側面印有細小的 Sennheiser 標示，小編頗喜歡低調的設計</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1205334 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身用上了磨砂質地，不易留下指紋等污漬</p><h2><strong>耳罩不焗促 </strong><strong>佩戴感舒適</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 包裝簡單，省卻了收納袋和盒，隨機會附送  1 條 USB-C 充電線。ACCENTUM Wireless 是頭罩式耳機，有一定份量，機身只重 22.2 克，小編戴了 3 小時未感不適，耳罩用料記憶綿，不感焗促外，亦舒服穩陣，不會輕易掉下。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205328 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩用料記憶綿，不感焗促外，亦舒服穩陣</p><h2><strong>保留實體鍵，感覺實在</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 使用了實體鍵，而非旗艦耳機的輕觸式設計，小編反而覺得幾好，一方面操控相對直接容易，按下更有實感，另一方面可確保不會誤觸。操控方面頗為簡單，最底在 USB-C 充電口旁的按鍵是開關掣，長按 3 秒可開關，5 秒則可連接藍牙，連接速度快。對上 3 粒按鍵，由上而下分別是大聲，暫停或播放音樂及細聲。惟一要投訴的，是欠缺了切換主動降噪和通透模式按鍵。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205330 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲實體鍵操控相對直接容易，按下更有實感</p><h2><strong>Sennheiser Smart Control </strong><strong>自定義 </strong><strong>EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 向來都有自家應用程式，用家可以下載 Smart Control，調整主動降噪、通透模式、EQ 等。主動降噪可選擇開啟或關閉減少風聲。EQ 方面就預設 2 項，分別是 Bass Boost 及 Podcast，假如用家對 EQ 未有太多認識，或許未能滿足需求。Sennheiser 似乎鼓勵用家自行調節。用家亦可自定通話時，聆聽多少自己的聲音。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205371 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205372 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-694x492.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="492" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-694x492.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-768x544.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可切換 ANC 及通透模式</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205373 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-309x580.jpg" alt="" width="309" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-309x580.jpg 309w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-480x900.jpg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-768x1440.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-819x1536.jpg 819w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 309px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可調 EQ</p><h2><strong>多裝置連接</strong></h2><p>Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless 有多裝置連接，用家可同時連上電腦及手機，小編工作時經常不止用一個裝置，所以覺得這功能非常實用。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205370 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-292x580.jpg" alt="" width="292" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-292x580.jpg 292w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-453x900.jpg 453w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-768x1527.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-773x1536.jpg 773w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2.jpg 805w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 292px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless 有多裝置連接</p><h2><strong>支援快速充電，充電</strong><strong> 10 分鐘可用 5 小時</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">續航力方面，充滿電的 ACCENTUM Wireless 可以連續使用 50 小時，起長的使用時間足夠小編長時使用 4 至 5 日。ACCENTUM Wireless 支援快速充電，只要充電 10 分鐘，即可使用 5 小時，可謂是驚人。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205329 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充滿電的 ACCENTUM Wireless 可以連續使用 50 小時，快速充電，只要充電 10 分鐘，即可使用 5 小時</p><h2><strong>通話表現良好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">由於可在 Sennheiser Smart Control 內調整聆聽多少自己的聲音，加上有 Hybrid ANC，因此 ACCENTUM Wireless 通話表現良好，如果在室內通話絕對沒問題，室外可能會有少許風噪聲。Jabra Elite 5 使用，了 SBC、AAC 以及 aptX，全都是基本配置，在 Android 手機上收聽理論上會好一點，但音樂來源亦會影響音色。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205331 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hybrid ANC 室內通話絕對沒問題</p><h2><strong>人聲</strong><strong>低頻</strong><strong>柔和 </strong><strong>三頻平衡好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小編在 iPhone 上使用 Moov 播放鄧麗欣的《他不准我哭》，人聲靠近突出，音色甜美。再試試陳奕迅的《富士山下》，不止人聲出色，音樂的分析力就不俗，清楚聽到配樂組合，低音結他和鼓聲不會突兀，很柔和，力度份量剛好。喜歡重低音的用家可自行設置 EQ，令低頻更突出。小編認為 ACCENTUM Wireless 適合聽流行歌，未必適合聽多配樂，多層次的搖滾音樂。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鄧麗欣《他不准我哭》</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陳奕迅《富士山下》</p><h2><strong>總結：音色出眾 </strong><strong>電量夠</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 的售價為 HK$ 1499，屬中價位，但做到高水準，的確有 Sennheiser 的高級感和音色，再加上續航力達 50 小時。如此的規格，性價比極高，適合有要求，長時間使用者。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

